query: SELECT tc.id, tc.channelName, COUNT(tm.id) as msg_count FROM telegram_channels tc LEFT JOIN telegram_messages tm ON tc.id = tm.channelId GROUP BY tc.id, tc.channelName ORDER BY msg_count DESC LIMIT 10
